text: Frobisher may refer to: ==People== * Frobisher (surname), a surname shared by several real and fictional people ==Places== * Frobisher, Saskatchewan * Frobisher Bay, a bay in Baffin Island, named after Martin Frobisher * Frobisher Bay, the former name of a town in Baffin Island, Canada, now known as Iqaluit * Frobisher Lake, a lake in central Saskatchewan ==Other uses== * Frobisher (Doctor Who), a character from the comic strips based on the television series Doctor Who * Robert Frobisher, a character from David Mitchell's novel Cloud Atlas * HMS Frobisher, two ships of the Royal Navy * Frobisher Says, a video game
title: Frobisher
